videos.description: Bradley Beal crosses up Terrence Ross to get into the paint, and then finishes through contact from Nikola Vucevic for the basket plus the foul.

videos.description: Markelle Fultz pours in a career-high 26 points, and the Magic outscore the Wizards 43-19 in the fourth quarter to earn their third straight win to start the year.
